 PP&E 
¶  Key formulae vs. “table” 
PPEEB = PPEBB + Acquisitions – Disposals 
• 
AccDepEB = AccDepBB + Depreciation – AccDepDisposal 
• 
MV / Proceeds from sales = BV + gain/loss 
